description: Shane Seeker`s Psyduck is blue colored as it is a Shiny Pokémon. It was the first ever Pokémon that he`d caught. Pikachu rescued it from the inside a Cofagrigus at the Colossus Ruins at the Desert Resort in the Unova region. It then helped in the Raid Battle against Golurk but was knocked out.
name: Koduck (Colorvar)
